CHANGELOG

Release 1.3 - TBD

* Feature: Services are now shut down in parallel, which is significantly faster.
* Feature: Internal checks are done every second, for config file changes and service processes.
* Feature: Service process check timer can be configured separately with a new directive (default is every second).
* Code:    .NET Framework dependency updated to 4.7.2.


Release 1.2 - 2018-12-29

* Fixes:   Email improvements (utf8 support etc)


Release 1.1 - 2018-11-20

* Code:    Code cleanup
* Code:    Builds have version numbers and use proper releases
* Feature: Comments can be used in definition lines now as well
